Amelia Rose https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amelia_Rose 0 Amelia Rose Blaire (born November 20, 1987) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as vampire Willa Burrell on the HBO series True Blood and Piper Shaw on the MTV series Scream. Amelia_Rose_Blaire ( born November_20_,_1987 ) is an_American_actress .
